<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٤٩٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5771">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللهِ الْأَنْصَارِيُّ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1647">حُمَيْدٌ: </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a>حَدَّثَهُمْ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«كِتَابُ اللهِ الْقِصَاصُ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>